overview.en: EUSD Token is a utility token. It isthe native token for ETrading Stablechain to pay for tx/gas fee and Liquidity Mining. ETrading Stablechain is a POS blockchain that is compatible with EVM. EUSD seeks to provide price stability with elastic supply monetary model, governable treasury.
overview.zh: EUSD代幣是一種功能型代幣。它是ETrading穩定鏈的母鏈代幣，同時能夠參與流動性挖礦。ETrading穩定鏈是一條和以太坊虛擬機兼容的POS的區塊鏈。EUSD希望能夠通過彈性的供給模型，可治理的儲備來實現價值的穩定。
